  "texts": [
    "In the session, students were reminded several times that they were free to use the example prompts provided or to craft their own prompts when interacting with ChatGPT.",
    "An example of these embedded prompts can be found in Fig. 3.",
    "The complete guide with all prompt examples is available in the supplementary resources.",
    "To answer the first research question, which explores students' ChatGPT interaction profiles, a thematic analysis was conducted on their conversation histories based on the approach defined by Clarke and Braun (2017).",
    "Two researchers first independently coded each student prompt within a conversation according to its purpose."
